    cpp:hasUptakeEfficiency "The sub peptide14â39 is directed to the nuclear region within 20 min, similar to synthetic CPP-Ts. It presented nuclear localization in rat cardiomyocytes and rat hepatocytes; the sub-peptide was unable to cross the cell membrane in all the six normal immortalized cell lines(HUV-EC-C, HFF-1, MCR-5, HEK-293, BHK-21 and MDCK) and  it was internalized and directed to the intranuclear region in all six neoplastic cell lines analyzed (SK-MEL-188, HEP G2,Caco-2, MDA-MB-231, A549 and DU 145)"@en .

