    cpp:hasUptakeEfficiency "The percentage of cell uptake (60%) and the median fluorescence intensity of the PEG12KL4/mRNA were significantly higher than that of naked mRNA and KL4/mRNA (15% uptake) complexes, while naked mRNA could not enter the cells."@en,
        "the KL4/siRNA complexes had significantly lower cellular uptake  compared to Lipofectamine 2000/siRNA complexes (95% uptake) , but in presence of 1 mg/ml of Infasurf for KL4/siRNA complexes uptake decreased from 70% to just over 40% while that for when Lipofectamine 2000/siRNA complexes reduced to below 5%."@en .

