        "Penetramax (0.95 Â± 0.11 pmol, p < 0.001) significantly enhanced the cellular insulin uptake when compared to insulin alone (0.21 Â± 0.04 pmol) while no increase in cellular uptake of lipidated insulin (0.33 Â± 0.08 pmol)."@en,
