        "LK-4-domain Z showed higher IgG delivery efficiency than LK-2-domain Z at every concentration point"@en,
        "miRNA 2861 alone showed 2.93% cellular uptake at 50 nM. By contrast, combination of 50 nM FAM-miRNA 2861 and 300 nM ac-LK resulted in 86.5% fluorescence-positive cells and A combination of 50 nM FAM-miRNA 2861 and 600 nM ac-LK resulted in 94.9% fluorescence-positive cells. However, in the lipofectamine group, only 42.6% of cells were positive for fluorescence."@en .

