    cpp:hasSequence "rrrrrrrrc"^^xsd:string ;
    cpp:hasUptakeEfficiency "Higher than RIPL R8"@en,
        "Liposomes modified with both HP (CCK8) and CPP (R8) peptides showed a slightly higher fluorescence intensity than the R8-LPs and CCK8-LPs and higher than the untargeted LPs."@en,
        "P-D-R8 showed enhanced cellular uptake with 1.44-fold higher than PD at 4 h."@en,
        "R8PECL can increase the uptake by more than 12-fold."@en,
        "Uptake of P-R8-Pho NPs on Caco-2 cells was about 3-fold higher than the control P NPs and almost the same level as P-R8 NPs. In E12 cells, P-R8-Pho NPs exhibited 1.65-fold and 3.4-fold higher uptake than that of P-R8 and P NPs, and P-R8 NPs was only 2-fold higher than that of the control P NPs."@en .

