    cpp:hasSequence "PFVYLI"^^xsd:string ;
    cpp:hasUptakeEfficiency "About 4 to 5 times higher concentration than the control polymer REF"@en,
        "Cou6 level for PFV-Lip-Cou6 was 2.3-fold higher than that of Lip-Cou6"@en,
        "CsA internalization was 4.7-fold higher for PFV and 6.8-fold higher for VPT in HeLa cells; 5.6-fold higher for PFV and 19.1-fold higher for VPT in MCF-7 cells"@en,
        "Efficient delivery of PTD-IVT-mRNA of SCO2 was confirmed in 30 min"@en,
        "R9F2Tf-liposomes showed a superior ability to induce GFP expression in bEnd.3 (41.4% versus 24.1% for PFTf-lip), glial (25.8% versus 22.9% for PFTf-lip), and primary neuronal cells (13.9% versus 12.0% for PFTf-lip)."@en,
        "Targeted daunorubicin and dioscin codelivery liposomes exhibited higher intracellular fluorescence than the other liposomal groups."@en,
        "The Dox uptake from the Tf-PFV liposomes showed approximately 66%, 66%, and 65% and Erlo was found to be approximately 69%, 68%, and 64% in U87, bEnd.3, and Primary glial cells, respectively. Tf-PFV liposomes showed significantly higher (p < 0.05) cellular uptake compared to single ligand or plain liposomes."@en .

